mil.navy.nrl.cmf.sousa.spatiotemporal
Class Vector3d

java.lang.Object
  mil.navy.nrl.cmf.sousa.spatiotemporal.Vector3d
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, mil.navy.nrl.cmf.stk.XYZd
public class Vector3d
extends Object
implements Serializable, mil.navy.nrl.cmf.stk.XYZd

Vector3d is a partial reimplementation of javax.vecmath.Vector3d. It exists to provide the funcionality if javax.vecmath.Vector3d without requiring Java3D.
